*Jedinice* su redovne vojne postrojbe. (Units are regular military formations.)

Do sada su *jedinice* uspešno sprovele misiju. (So far, units have successfully carried out the mission.)

Vojska je angažovala nekoliko *jedinica* za kontrolu. (The army has deployed several units for control.)

Policija je na terenu imala pojedinačne *jedinice*. (The police had individual units on the ground.)

Naša *jedinica* je prva stigla na mesto događaja. (Our unit was the first to arrive at the scene.)